snippet.title: FNAF Security Breach - Opening Cutscene
snippet.description:
FNAF Security Breach - Opening Cutscene 

Five Nights At Freddy's Security Breach on PlayStation 5
In this video I decided it would be cool to show the opening of Fnaf Security Breach because at the end you can notice that something wrong with Freddy, which is pretty easy to miss if you didn't full pay attention while playing.

This opening cutscene was not at all how I expected this game to open, but it was a pleasant surprise to see some of the characters look and act more realistic the expected!

This is an edited video that lets you watch the opening cutscene of Fight Nights at Freddy's Security breach, incase you miss the easily miss able easter eggs.

Capture with AVerMedia Live Gamer ULTRA with OBS

Edited with Davinci Resolve
